                </a>
                <a href="mailto:daniel_m_02@outlook.com" class="social-icon" aria-label="Email">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"></path></svg>
